    "Special Requests or Notes": "特别要求或说明",
    "This Pet Care Add-On gives you everything you need to run your business smoothly. Easily manage appointments, adoptions, services, and payments all in one place. Keep track of customers, pets, and packages with smart tools and simple dashboards. Customize your website, handle inquiries, and get real-time insights to grow your services with confidence.": "通过这个 Pet Care 附加功能,您可以轻松地管理预约,收养,服务和付款. 通过智能工具和简单的仪表板,跟踪客户,物和包裹. 定制您的网站,处理查询,并获得实时洞察力,以轻松地扩展您的服务.",
    "Simplify ": "简化",
    "Pet Care Management": "物护理管理",
    " with WorkDo Dash!": "通过WorkDoDash!",
    "From grooming appointments to adoptions and service tracking. Stay organized with centralized dashboards, manage customers and pets seamlessly, and streamline payments and inquiries—all within one powerful, easy-to-use system.": "通过集中式仪表板保持组织,无地管理客户和物,并简化支付和查询 - - 所有这些都在一个强大,易于使用的系统中实现.",
    "Build & Manage Pet Care Packages Seamlessly": "构建和管理物护理包",
    "Maintain a complete database of available pet vaccines with pricing and detailed descriptions, allowing easy management of vaccine inventory to ensure pet owners have access to essential health services. Design attractive grooming packages by combining multiple services and vaccines into comprehensive offerings, with automatic calculation of package totals while allowing manual adjustments for special pricing. Visual package icons and detailed descriptions help customers understand value propositions, while the flexible package builder accommodates various service combinations for creating seasonal offers and premium packages. Quick search functionality and export options help veterinarians and staff access vaccine information efficiently during consultations and treatment planning.": "保持可用的物疫苗的完整数据库,包括定价和详细描述,从而轻松管理疫苗库存,确保物所有者能够获得基本的医疗服务.通过将多个服务和疫苗组合成综合性产品,设计有吸引力的护理包,同时允许为特殊定价进行手动调整.视觉包图标和详细描述帮助客户了解价值建议,而灵活的包构建器可以容纳各种服务组合,以创建季节性优惠和优惠包.快速搜索功能和出口选项可以帮助兽医和工作人员在咨询和治疗规划期间高效地访问疫苗信息.",
    "Pet Adoption & Adoption Requests Made Effortless": "物收养和收养申请变得简单",
    "Complete pet adoption system manages available pets with detailed profiles including health status, classification tags, and multiple images, tracking adoption availability and managing adoption requests efficiently. The system handles adoption amounts, pet characteristics, and availability status, making it easy for potential adopters to find suitable pets while maintaining organized records. Manage adoption requests with complete applicant information and status tracking, processing requests from initial submission through approval and completion stages. Integration with payment processing ensures smooth adoption fee collection, while detailed request tracking helps staff manage the adoption process efficiently while maintaining communication with potential adopters.": "完整的物收养系统管理可用物,包括健康状况,分类标签和多个图像,有效地跟踪收养可用性和管理收养请求. 该系统处理收养数量,物特征和可用性状态,使潜在收养者在保持有组织的记录的同时轻松找到合适的物. 管理收养请求,提供完整的申请人信息和状态跟踪,从初始提交到批准和完成阶段处理请求. 与付款处理的集成确保了顺利收取收养费的详细信息,而请求跟踪有助于员工在与潜在收养者保持沟通的同时有效地管理收养过程.",
    "Complete Appointment Management": "完整的预约管理",
    "Streamline appointment booking with comprehensive customer and pet information collection. The appointment system captures owner details, pet information, and service requirements in a single integrated form. Staff assignment features enable proper workload distribution and scheduling management. Appointment status tracking includes pending, approved, completed, and rejected states with automated billing integration. The system generates unique appointment numbers and provides detailed appointment history for customer service excellence.": "简化预约预约,采用全面的客户和物信息收集.预约系统以单一的集成形式捕获所有者详细信息,物信息和服务要求.员工分配功能使工作负载分配和调度管理得以正常进行.预约状态跟踪包括待定,批准,完成和拒绝状态,并自动化计费集成.系统生成独特的预约号码,并为客户服务卓越提供详细的预约历史.预约系统可提供预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,预约数据,",
    "Integrated Payment Processing": "综合支付处理",
    "Manage all financial transactions through a comprehensive billing and payment system. Process payments for approved appointments with multiple payment method support, including cash, bank transfers, and checks. The system tracks payment status, due amounts, and generates detailed payment summaries. Payment record management includes receipt uploads, reference tracking, and comprehensive payment history. Automated payment calculations ensure accurate billing based on selected services and packages.": "通过全面的计费和支付系统管理所有金融交易.处理已批准的预约的支付,支持多种支付方式,包括现金,银行转账和支票.系统跟踪支付状态,应付金额并生成详细的支付总结.支付记录管理包括收据上传,参考跟踪和全面的支付历史记录.自动支付计算确保基于选择的服务和包的准确计费.",
    "Complete Frontend Website Management": "完整的前端网站管理",
    "Handle customer inquiries and communications through an integrated contact management system that tracks message status from new inquiries through resolution, categorizing communications appropriately while managing visitor submissions from the website. Powerful configuration system allows complete customization of website appearance and functionality, managing brand elements, banner settings, review systems, and payment policies. Configure contact information, social media links, and FAQ sections with granular control over what content appears on the website, ensuring consistent branding and user experience across all pages while maintaining a comprehensive customer communication history.": "通过集成的联系管理系统处理客户查询和通信,通过解决方案跟踪新查询的消息状态,在管理网站访问者提交时适当分类通信. 强大的配置系统允许完全定制网站外观和功能,管理品牌元素,横幅设置,评论系统和支付策略. 配置联系信息,社交媒体链接和常见问题部分,对网站上显示的内容进行细分控制,确保在所有页面上保持一致的品牌和用户体验,同时保持全面的客户通信历史.",
